    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【掉SAN预警，本游戏含有一些比较掉SAN的内容，比如触手啊，触手啊，还有触手啊什么的，游玩前请确保自己能接受。什么？就好这口？那没事了。】</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【然后，这里没有那种……就是那种……被这样那样的内容，真的没有哦！不信？不信就算了。】</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏剧情</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们可爱的魔女缪可苏路过了一个魔物洞穴，于是她准备进去逛逛。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她是要做什么呢？为了寻找深埋的宝藏赚钱？还是讨伐盘踞于此的魔物？都不是，她只是来逛逛而已~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265880/extras/9dc424b13e16ba87dc666e9f5fb4e32d.avif?t=1733277722\" width=260 height=236 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【好无聊的剧情啊！】</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >守护人类什么的才不关心呢，只要有乐子就行了~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法介绍</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏玩法？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >嗯…………</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >就是，肉鸽啦，卡组构建啦，然后战斗中通过拼点什么的来进攻。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >很好理解的！简单易上手！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >试玩版可以去墨元素的b站主页找找！（因为被ban过一次所以不敢再审一个试玩了）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >好吧，当然还是要认真介绍一下的~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个回合，当双方都出同类型的进攻牌时，就要进行拼点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265880/extras/35d814fddc0a0778564edcb8258fdf4d.avif?t=1733277722\" width=260 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只有点数大的才能进攻，很好理解的玩法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而本游戏的特色，<strong>闪避牌</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265880/extras/b463c700e604112e438c7a5805ba9b09.avif?t=1733277722\" width=206 height=284 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当你的点数比对方小时，也不是只能挨打。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用闪避牌会让你在点数比对方小时闪避掉对方的攻击，以柔克刚！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >好好利用好你的闪避牌，不管敌人伤害多高都不怕。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏含有190+不同的卡牌与180+宝物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还有，各种可爱的魔物娘！就凭这个也该来玩玩了吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265880/extras/27c1e7301913946abc8ca2f9f3b1b5a7.avif?t=1733277722\" width=485 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
